00:00:59.530 --> 00:01:03.270
I am here to talk about
my new book and the way

00:01:03.270 --> 00:01:05.099
a magician thinks.

00:01:05.099 --> 00:01:07.770
And this is a very
exciting for me.

00:01:07.770 --> 00:01:10.890
I've really just given
